_sText:
This is medium size dust themed map.
Download contains fully working radar with map parts named (CT / T Spawn , Bombsite A / B , Long Hall , Middle , House , Side. )
Layout is very simple.
All install instruction are in download
Original map size is 7,21 mb, but WinRar compression.
One mosque have small crack on wall and you can enter and go under it.
That is not showed on overview in game or here on screenshots. But I drawed two red lines so you can imagine that as small underpass how is that map part called.

Report any bugs or glitches here, I spot them but I will fix them in second version
